---
// Hero Section - Astro component (zero-JS)
---

<section class="w-full py-20 px-4 bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-50 to-slate-100">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-8">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-slate-900 leading-tight">
        Expert Electronics Repair in Los Mochis
      </h1>
      <p class="text-2xl text-slate-700 font-semibold">
        Trusted for 15 Years
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Fast Service for Cellphones, Computers, and Gaming Consoles
      </p>
    </div>

    <a
      href="https://wa.me/526241234567?text=I%20need%20a%20repair%20quote"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
      class="inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-lg text-lg transition-colors duration-200 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl"
    >
      Request Repair Quote via WhatsApp
    </a>
